content.rendered:
HEYYYY!! Here are my current favorite songs to workout to! I linked each song out to its YouTube vid so you can listen straight from here. Would love to know what songs are your fav, or if you want to share your playlist with me!! I love new music!

MY TOP WORKOUT SONGS:

Put Me On Somethin’ – P-LO ft. E 40

Get It Right – Tidus

You Make Me – Chelsea Cutler

U-RITE – THEY

Sauce It Up – Lil Uzi Vert

The Best You Had – Nina Nesbitt

Questions – Chris Brown

New Rules – Dua Lipa

Show Me – John Splithoff ft. Madison Ryann Ward

Run It Up – Dame DOLLA ft. Lil Wayne

Mine – Bazzi

Self-Made – Bryson Tiller

Feel It Still – Portugal. The Man

When it Rains It Pours – Luke Combs

No Limitations – Tidus

Space – TK Kravitz ft. Sexton

Rake It Up – Yo Gotti ft. Nicki Minaj

Silence – Marshmello ft. Khalid

No Limit – G Eazy

The Shine – ayokay ft. Chelsea Cutler

Wylin’ – Always Never

Sorry Not Sorry – Demi Lovato

Strip That Down – Liam Payne ft. Quavo

Friends – Remix, Justin Bieber and Julia Michaels

Let Me Go – Hailee Steinfield & Alesso

Butterfly Effect – Travis Scott
